com.swfm.mica
Class MiShapePopupMenu

java.lang.Object
  com.swfm.mica.MiEditorMenu
      com.swfm.mica.MiShapePopupMenu
All Implemented Interfaces:
MiiCommandNames, MiiContextMenu, MiiDisplayNames, MiiMessages
public class MiShapePopupMenu
extends MiEditorMenu
implements MiiCommandNames, MiiMessages

This class makes a 'shape popup' menu that is suitable for adding to shapes as their context menu. Each menu item has status bar and balloon help and most have accelerators and mnemonics.

When a menu item is selected by the user one of the following commands are generated: 

    Mi_CUT_COMMAND_NAME
    Mi_COPY_COMMAND_NAME
    Mi_DELETE_COMMAND_NAME
    Mi_DUPLICATE_COMMAND_NAME
    Mi_DISCONNECT_COMMAND_NAME
    Mi_BRING_TO_FRONT_COMMAND_NAME
    Mi_SEND_TO_BACK_COMMAND_NAME
    Mi_SEND_BACKWARD_COMMAND_NAME
    Mi_DISPLAY_PROPERTIES_COMMAND_NAME

Version:
%I% %G%
Author:
Michael L. Davis
See Also:
MiiContextMenu, MiPart.setContextMenu(com.swfm.mica.MiiContextMenu)
